## âœ¨ What This Does

Agentic Reliability Framework is a **production-ready AI system** that:

âœ… **Detects anomalies** before they impact customers (milliseconds, not hours)  
âœ… **Diagnoses root causes** automatically with evidence-based reasoning  
âœ… **Predicts future failures** using time-series forecasting  
âœ… **Self-heals** without human intervention through policy-based automation  

**Built with Fortune 500 reliability patterns. Tested in production.**

